Allianz Asset Management of America L.P. Key Developments

PIMCO Presents at 18th Annual US Real Estate Opportunity & Private Funds Investing Forum 2017, Jun-25-2017 through Jun-27-2017
Jun 22 17
PIMCO Presents at 18th Annual US Real Estate Opportunity & Private Funds Investing Forum 2017, Jun-25-2017 through Jun-27-2017. Venue: Newport, Rhode Island, United States. Presentation Date & Speakers: Jun-26-2017, Kevin Morgenroth, Senior Vice President. Jun-27-2017, PAUL VOSPER, Executive Vice President.


Pimco Announces Executive Changes
Jun 16 17
Pimco has appointed Robin Shanahan and Peter Strelow as co-chief operating officers. They will report to CEO Emmanuel Roman. They will replace Pimco's president Jay Jacobs, is set to retire on September 30. Strelow is currently the global head, funds and chief administrative officer and Shanahan is the global head of human resources.


PIMCO Presents at Managed Funds Association Forum 2017, Jun-20-2017 03:25 PM
Jun 13 17
PIMCO Presents at Managed Funds Association Forum 2017, Jun-20-2017 03:25 PM. Venue: Four Seasons Hotel Chicago, Chicago, Illinois, United States. Speakers: Nicholas J. Johnson, Head of Quantitative Strategies Portfolio Management.


